com.stormpath.sdk.api

Interface ApiKeyCriteria

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ApiKeyOptions<ApiKeyCriteria>, Criteria<ApiKeyCriteria>, Options

    public interface ApiKeyCriteria
extends Criteria<ApiKeyCriteria>, ApiKeyOptions<ApiKeyCriteria>
    An ApiKey-specific Criteria class, enabling an ApiKey-specific fluentquery DSL. ApiKeyCriteria instances can be constructed by using the ApiKeys utility class, for example: 
     ApiKeys.criteria()
     .offsetBy(50)
     .limitTo(25)
     .withTenant()
     .withAccount();
    Since:
    1.0.RC
